WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.204
Myocarditis — inflammation of the myocardium —

00:00:03.204 --> 00:00:06.409
represents one of cardiology's most clinically challenging

00:00:06.409 --> 00:00:06.867
diagnoses.

00:00:06.867 --> 00:00:10.071
Its adverse effects range from self-limited chest

00:00:10.071 --> 00:00:13.276
pain to fulminant cardiogenic shock and sudden

00:00:13.276 --> 00:00:14.191
cardiac death.

00:00:14.191 --> 00:00:17.396
This presentation reviews the pathophysiology, clinical consequences,

00:00:17.396 --> 00:00:20.600
and risk stratification essential for practicing physicians.
